data.description:
Welcome to 1120 S Zane Hwy in charming Martins Ferry, OH! This impeccably crafted home is a true gem, boasting a perfect blend of modern updates and classic charm. Step into a welcoming ambiance where every detail has been carefully curated to create a harmonious living space.

The heart of this home is undoubtedly the beautiful deck that beckons you to unwind and entertain. Picture yourself enjoying tranquil evenings around the fire pit, creating lasting memories. This outdoor oasis is the epitome of relaxation, offering a seamless transition between indoor and outdoor living.

As you explore the interiors, you'll be captivated by the thoughtful updates throughout. The metal roof not only adds a touch of contemporary elegance but also ensures durability for years to come. The updated floors showcase a modern aesthetic, providing a stylish foundation for your personal touch.

Discover a home where every corner tells a story of comfort and style. The layout is designed to cater to both daily living and entertaining, making it a versatile haven for all occasions. With its prime location in Martins Ferry, you'll enjoy the convenience of nearby amenities while savoring the tranquility of this welcoming neighborhood.

Immerse yourself in the warmth of this home and envision the possibilities that await. Schedule a showing today and experience the seamless fusion of timeless character and contemporary living. Welcome home!
